text: 678 () is a 2010 Egyptian drama movie. It is about sexual harassment of women in Egypt. It was produced by Bushra Rozza. The movie has a rating of 80% on Rotten Tomatoes. Nelly, one of the movie's main characters, is based upon an Egyptian woman called Noha Roshdy who prosecuted her harasser in 2008.Acclaimed Movie "678" Shows the Ubiquity of Sexual Harassment in Egypt ==References== Category:2010 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies
